Terrorsaur:





The forest was full of shadows. It still held its errie feel. 
He could tell Rowdy Wolf was still around. He backed up. He thought 
he could see him, but he was only a shadow, a heavy shouldered 
figure. He backed into another tree. Rowdy Wolf was glaring at him, 
facing him from a distance. He thought of a way to get back to the 
cave safely.
